summary: Update to GCC 4.6.0:   * Modify the builder to not fail when a static library is in $out/libexec/gcc/*/*   * Disable libquadmath when building a static-only bootstrap of GCC, see http://gcc.gnu.org/ml/gcc/2011-03/msg00465.html   * Add handling for cloog if it is passed in in place of cloog-ppl
